description: This file defines data models, agents, and a team setup for a national park adventure planning system. It includes class definitions for park details, agent configurations for planning and weather, and a team that combines these components to generate park itineraries.

classes.name: NationalParkAdventure
classes.description: Data model representing detailed information about a national park, including attractions, trails, wildlife, safety, and other features.

methods.name: run
methods.description: Executes the team to generate a response based on a prompt asking for a park itinerary.
